{"tid":1361781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劉細良：政府期待騷亂、暴動，甚至人命傷亡","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T17:09:57.000Z","uid":127708,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4fe6774e95449177b431f3b8da47a609f20e853e","tid":1361781,"uid":127708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/379296896114849?s=100002437125470&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F127745917936616%2Fposts%2F379296896114849%3Fs%3D100002437125470%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0EYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=cdf267a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/127745917936616/posts/379296896114849?s=100002437125470&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n分析得好 值得睇<br />\n元朗單野我都好嬲<br />\n但冷靜過後，我都認同<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果7.27我地衝，一有人命傷亡，我地就輸了</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冷靜再冷靜<br />\n忍一次咁多<br />\n<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"831a8a98664581c23a344720f03c9d530478d563","tid":1361781,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"或者咁講，就算真係佢預期的畫面<br />\n但結果未必佢可以操控到<br />\n<br />\n訊息流通咁快的年代<br />\n所有陰招見曬光"},{"pid":"dd217b197da2367d68a30f12dae9e1aa9b245970","tid":1361781,"uid":108571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"一向有聽<br />\n好驚佢被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870874f5436f9151ae668ec894044a1370cc229b","tid":1361781,"uid":270954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff9232d3c5842dbea986737ae8d40d06bb864cc","tid":1361781,"uid":13076,"like":0,"dislike":